<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .alert-box { border: 1px solid #d9534f; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f2f4; border-radius: 5px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #d9534f; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="alert-box">
        <h2 style="color: #d9534f;">⚠️ Overdue Work Order Alert</h2>
        <p>Dear Maintenance Team,</p>
        <p>The following work order is past its due date and requires immediate attention:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Work Order ID:</strong> {{ WorkOrderId }}</li>
            <li><strong>Aircraft ID:</strong> {{ AircraftId }}</li>
            <li><strong>Aircraft Tail:</strong> {{ TailNumber | default: "N/A" }}</li>
            <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{ Description | default: "No description provided" }}</li>
        </ul>
        {% if Url != "" %}
            <p><a href="{{ Url }}" class="btn">View Work Order in System</a></p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</body>
</html>